description: Exceptional sunlit one-bedroom condo in South Boston, recently renovated to perfection. The modern kitchen seamlessly flows into the living and dining area, showcasing stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a tiled backsplash, and a built-in wine holder. The spacious bedroom boasts ample closet space and opens to a back porch with a sitting area. Additional highlights comprise an updated bathroom with a granite vanity, hardwood floors, and high ceilings throughout. Dedicated storage located in lower level. Conveniently located near the red line, Carson Beach, and easy highway access.
